            <h2>Health risks of sewer emergencies</h2>
            <p>Sewer emergencies are not just inconvenient — they pose real health risks that make fast response critical.</p>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Raw sewage contains bacteria, viruses, and parasites that cause serious illness</li>
              <li>Sewer gas (hydrogen sulfide and methane) is toxic at concentrated levels</li>
              <li>Standing sewage water breeds mold within 24 to 48 hours</li>
              <li>Contaminated surfaces require professional sanitization</li>
              <li>Children, elderly, and immunocompromised individuals are at higher risk</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
