            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Water damage to flooring, drywall, and personal belongings</li>
              <li>Foundation erosion from leaking sewage undermining the soil</li>
              <li>Landscape destruction as sinkholes expand and soil becomes contaminated</li>
              <li>Escalating repair costs — a spot repair becomes a full replacement</li>
              <li>Insurance complications when damage is not mitigated promptly</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
