          <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item"><button type="button" aria-expanded="false">How quickly can Honest Drain respond to a sewer emergency?</button><div><p>We prioritize emergency calls and dispatch the nearest available technician immediately. Response times depend on your location and current demand, but we treat every sewer emergency as urgent.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item"><button type="button" aria-expanded="false">What should I do while waiting for the technician?</button><div><p>Stop using all water in the home — do not flush toilets, run sinks, or use the washing machine. Keep family and pets away from any sewage. Do not attempt to clear the blockage yourself. Our dispatcher will guide you through additional steps specific to your situation.</p></div></div>
